OL,3,CPolice force pays #9,000 in damages to
OL,4,Cveteran for 'false imprisonment'
OL,6,FA former military police officer has
OL,7,Fbeen paid almost #9,000 in damages by
OL,8,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) after
OL,9,Fbeing locked in custody for almost 12
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,12,FPaul Nugent, 62, was arrested after a
OL,13,Frow with a woman at his Heywood home
OL,14,Fin January 2020 when police were
OL,15,Fcalled.
