OL,3,CPolice force pays #9,000 in damages to
OL,4,Cveteran for 'false imprisonment'
OL,6,FThe security consultant claimed he was
OL,7,Frepeatedly assaulted by the woman, but
OL,8,Flater said he found out by using a
OL,9,F'subject access request' (SAR) to
OL,10,Faccess police reports that he had been
OL,11,Fidentified as 'a high-risk abuse
OL,12,Fperpetrator' by a police officer he
OL,13,Fhad never met.
