OL,3,CPolice force pays #9,000 in damages to
OL,4,Cveteran for 'false imprisonment'
OL,6,FMr Nugent said that he was driven to
OL,7,Fthe brink of suicide as a result of
OL,8,Fallegations that he sexually assaulted
OL,9,Fthe woman over an eight-month period,
OL,10,Fhowever, he claims he was working in
OL,11,FBulgaria for five of those eight
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FMr Nugent said evidence of his absence
OL,15,Ffrom the country, which he offered to
OL,16,FRochdale GMP's investigators, was not
OL,17,Fcompiled.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
