OL,3,CPolice force pays #9,000 in damages to
OL,4,Cveteran for 'false imprisonment'
OL,6,FHe claims that on three occasions
OL,7,Fbetween May 2019 and March 2021,
OL,8,Fpolice attempted to bring charges for
OL,9,Fsexual assault against him, but in
OL,10,Feach case, the Crown Prosecution
OL,11,FService said there was no evidence to
OL,12,Fcharge him.
OL,14,FMr Nugent said: "As of today, I have
OL,15,Fnever been charged, cautioned, or
OL,16,Fwarned by the police for any crime
OL,17,Fwhatsoever."
