OL,3,CPolice force pays #9,000 in damages to
OL,4,Cveteran for 'false imprisonment'
OL,6,FHe claims he has spent more than
OL,7,F#20,000 on trying to clear his name,
OL,8,Fincluding hiring a private
OL,9,Finvestigator.
OL,11,F"Not one piece of evidence I pointed
OL,12,Fthe police to in order to establish my
OL,13,Finnocence was investigated by Rochdale
OL,14,FGMP," Mr Nugent said.
OL,16,F"How they can arrest someone and then
OL,17,Fnot investigate their evidence and
OL,18,Fjust send them away is so very wrong.
OL,19,FI am suffering from the stigma of
OL,20,Fbeing arrested for such an offence.
