OL,3,CPolice force pays #9,000 in damages to
OL,4,Cveteran for 'false imprisonment'
OL,6,F"Police have destroyed my whole life
OL,7,Fbecause they failed to do their job
OL,8,Fcorrectly. Their treatment of me has
OL,9,Fleft me feeling I can no longer trust
OL,10,Fthem."
OL,12,FMr Nugent said he has undergone
OL,13,Fcounselling for anxiety, fear and post-
OL,14,Ftraumatic stress disorder (PTSD) and
OL,15,Fspoke of his 'darkest moments' when he
OL,16,Fcontemplated taking his own life.
